<package version="1.0">
    <name>XML_Feed_Parser</name>
    <summary>Providing a somewhat unified API for handling </summary>
    <description>XML_Feed_Parser is a parser for (the various) RSS and Atom format XML feeds. It attempts to provide a somewhat unified API while still allowing access to the full details of each feed type.</description>
